title: Do As Infinity Discography (Do the Box)
description:
A complete collection of Do As Infinity's studio albums. This is pretty much what you would get in the "Do the Box" album box set. This batch contains many more songs outside of those albums, however, and even some lives (no live albums, though). 

Most of the songs are 160 kbps, some 128.

Album info: http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Do_as_infinity_discography#Albums
